      <when condition="@(context.Variables["filterVariable"] != null)">
        <set-query-parameter name="filter" exists-action="override">
          <value>@(string.Format("attributeId eq 'B1' and {0}", context.Variables["filterVariable"]))</value>
        </set-query-parameter>
      </when>
      <otherwise>
        <set-query-parameter name="filter" exists-action="override">
          <value>attributeId eq 'B1'</value>
        </set-query-parameter>
      </otherwise>
    </choose>

  </inbound>

    <base />

    <base />
  </outbound>

    <base />
  </on-error>

</policies>
